                            <comment id="13654451" author="mumrah" created="Fri, 10 May 2013 13:04:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Not sure how you guys prefer patches. This was generated with &quot;git diff --no-prefix HEAD&quot; from the camel-hdfs directory. Let me know if you prefer something else.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
